                <p>My research (see <a
                href="pubs/selected.html">selected publications</a>) has covered many topics in
                computational geometry and graph algorithms, including:</p>

                <ul>
                  <li>Graph drawing and information visualization</li>

		  <li>Dynamic graph algorithms and dynamic closest pair
		  data structures</li>

                  <li>Mesh generation and optimal triangulation</li>

		  <li>K-shortest paths and related combinatorial
		  enumeration algorithms</a>

		  <li>Subgraph isomorphism and network statistics</li>

                  <li>Data depth and robust statistics</li>

                  <li>Exponential-time algorithms for NP-hard problems</li>

		  <li>Distance-preserving embeddings of graphs and
		  metric spaces</li>
                </ul>

                <p>I am also an avid photographer and have many
                photos in my <a href="pix/">web photo
                gallery</a>.</p>

		<p>This site is quite static; if you want more frequent
		updates (or to find out what's changed here)
		go to my
		<a href="http://www.livejournal.com/users/11011110/">livejournal</a>
		or <a href="https://plus.google.com/100003628603413742554/posts">Google+</a>
		accounts.</p>

                <p>My name is not uncommon (although the spelling
                is atypical); see my page of <a href=
                "eppstein.html">Eppsteins on the net</a> if you
